name: Beetle of meaning
description:
In celebration of #HEN500k I want to share a beetle of meaning with you. 

I saw a big beautiful beetle struggling on his back not so long ago. I picked the tired being up and admired his beautiful form before putting him back where he belongs -in nature. It was a nice moment, caring for something so small. I thought about how all life matters in a moment of not feeling much worth myself. "How ironic I thought", concluding that my life must matter too.

Keep this piece for as long as you need a reminder that you matter. Pass it on to someone who needs it once the beetle has served its purpose.
